fields.question_text: What format is best for delivering a logo so that it may be scaled up or down without pixelization?
fields.name: What format is best to deliver a logo to a client
fields.explanation: Adobe Illustrator (.ai) files  and Embedded PostScript (.eps) files store images as vector graphics and therefore allow resizing without pixelization.
